{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.013.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-20: cf. 2 S 13:23-39. (2 S 12:1-7. 1 R 20:38-42.) \u00c9z 18:23.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Joab, fils de Tseruja, s\u2019aper\u00e7ut que le c\u0153ur du roi \u00e9tait port\u00e9 pour Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.2","name":"2 Samuel 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.13.39","name":"2 Samuel 13:39","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.13.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il envoya chercher \u00e0 Tekoa une femme habile, et il lui dit: Montre-toi d\u00e9sol\u00e9e, et rev\u00eats des habits de deuil; ne t\u2019oins pas d\u2019huile, et sois comme une femme qui depuis longtemps pleure un mort.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.3","name":"2 Samuel 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.1","name":"2 Samuel 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Tu iras ainsi vers le roi, et tu lui parleras de cette mani\u00e8re. Et Joab lui mit dans la bouche ce qu\u2019elle devait dire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.4","name":"2 Samuel 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.2","name":"2 Samuel 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>La femme de Tekoa alla parler au roi. Elle tomba la face contre terre et se prosterna, et elle dit: O roi, sauve-moi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.5","name":"2 Samuel 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.3","name":"2 Samuel 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Le roi lui dit: Qu\u2019as-tu? Elle r\u00e9pondit: Oui, je suis veuve, mon mari est mort!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.6","name":"2 Samuel 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.4","name":"2 Samuel 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Ta servante avait deux fils; ils se sont tous deux querell\u00e9s dans les champs, et il n\u2019y avait personne pour les s\u00e9parer; l\u2019un a frapp\u00e9 l\u2019autre, et l\u2019a tu\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.7","name":"2 Samuel 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.5","name":"2 Samuel 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et voici, toute la famille s\u2019est lev\u00e9e contre ta servante, en disant: Livre le meurtrier de son fr\u00e8re! Nous voulons le faire mourir, pour la vie de son fr\u00e8re qu\u2019il a tu\u00e9; nous voulons d\u00e9truire m\u00eame l\u2019h\u00e9ritier! Ils \u00e9teindraient ainsi le tison qui me reste, pour ne laisser \u00e0 mon mari ni nom ni survivant sur la face de la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.8","name":"2 Samuel 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.6","name":"2 Samuel 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 la femme: Va dans ta maison. Je donnerai des ordres \u00e0 ton sujet.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.9","name":"2 Samuel 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.7","name":"2 Samuel 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>La femme de Tekoa dit au roi: C\u2019est sur moi, \u00f4 roi mon seigneur, et sur la maison de mon p\u00e8re, que le ch\u00e2timent va tomber; le roi et son tr\u00f4ne n\u2019auront pas \u00e0 en souffrir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.10","name":"2 Samuel 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.8","name":"2 Samuel 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le roi dit: Si quelqu\u2019un parle contre toi, am\u00e8ne-le-moi, et il ne lui arrivera plus de te toucher.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.11","name":"2 Samuel 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.9","name":"2 Samuel 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Elle dit: Que le roi se souvienne de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, afin que le vengeur du sang n\u2019augmente pas la ruine, et qu\u2019on ne d\u00e9truise pas mon fils! Et il dit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant! Il ne tombera pas \u00e0 terre un cheveu de ton fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.12","name":"2 Samuel 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.10","name":"2 Samuel 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>La femme dit: Permets que ta servante dise un mot \u00e0 mon seigneur le roi. Et il dit: Parle!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.13","name":"2 Samuel 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.11","name":"2 Samuel 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>La femme dit: Pourquoi penses-tu de la sorte \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard du peuple de Dieu, puisqu\u2019il r\u00e9sulte des paroles m\u00eames du roi que le roi est comme coupable en ne rappelant pas celui qu\u2019il a proscrit?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.14","name":"2 Samuel 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.12","name":"2 Samuel 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il nous faut certainement mourir, et nous serons comme des eaux r\u00e9pandues \u00e0 terre et qui ne se rassemblent plus; Dieu n\u2019\u00f4te pas la vie, mais il d\u00e9sire que le fugitif ne reste pas banni de sa pr\u00e9sence.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.15","name":"2 Samuel 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.13","name":"2 Samuel 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Maintenant, si je suis venue dire ces choses au roi mon seigneur, c\u2019est que le peuple m\u2019a effray\u00e9e. Et ta servante a dit: Je veux parler au roi; peut-\u00eatre le roi fera-t-il ce que dira sa servante.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.16","name":"2 Samuel 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.14","name":"2 Samuel 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Oui, le roi \u00e9coutera sa servante, pour la d\u00e9livrer de la main de ceux qui cherchent \u00e0 nous exterminer, moi et mon fils, de l\u2019h\u00e9ritage de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.17","name":"2 Samuel 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.15","name":"2 Samuel 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Ta servante a dit: Que la parole de mon seigneur le roi me donne le repos. Car mon seigneur le roi est comme un ange de Dieu, pr\u00eat \u00e0 entendre le bien et le mal. Et que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, soit avec toi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.18","name":"2 Samuel 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.16","name":"2 Samuel 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le roi r\u00e9pondit, et dit \u00e0 la femme: Ne me cache pas ce que je vais te demander. Et la femme dit: Que mon seigneur le roi parle!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.19","name":"2 Samuel 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.17","name":"2 Samuel 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le roi dit alors: La main de Joab n\u2019est-elle pas avec toi dans tout ceci? Et la femme r\u00e9pondit: Aussi vrai que ton \u00e2me est vivante, \u00f4 roi mon seigneur, il n\u2019y a rien \u00e0 droite ni \u00e0 gauche de tout ce que dit mon seigneur le roi. C\u2019est, en effet, ton serviteur Joab qui m\u2019a donn\u00e9 des ordres, et qui a mis dans la bouche de ta servante toutes ces paroles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.20","name":"2 Samuel 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.18","name":"2 Samuel 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.20","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:20","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>C\u2019est pour donner \u00e0 la chose une autre tournure que ton serviteur Joab a fait cela. Mais mon seigneur est aussi sage qu\u2019un ange de Dieu, pour conna\u00eetre tout ce qui se passe sur la terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.21","name":"2 Samuel 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.19","name":"2 Samuel 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.21","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:21","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.022,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 21-33: cf. 2 S 13:37-39.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 Joab: Voici, je veux bien faire cela; va donc, ram\u00e8ne le jeune homme Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.22","name":"2 Samuel 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.20","name":"2 Samuel 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.22","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:22","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Joab tomba la face contre terre et se prosterna, et il b\u00e9nit le roi. Puis il dit: Ton serviteur conna\u00eet aujourd\u2019hui que j\u2019ai trouv\u00e9 gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 tes yeux, \u00f4 roi mon seigneur, puisque le roi agit selon la parole de son serviteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.23","name":"2 Samuel 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.21","name":"2 Samuel 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.23","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:23","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Et Joab se leva et partit pour Gueschur, et il ramena Absalom \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.24","name":"2 Samuel 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.22","name":"2 Samuel 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.24","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:24","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Mais le roi dit: Qu\u2019il se retire dans sa maison, et qu\u2019il ne voie point ma face. Et Absalom se retira dans sa maison, et il ne vit point la face du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.25","name":"2 Samuel 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.23","name":"2 Samuel 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.25","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:25","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Il n\u2019y avait pas un homme dans tout Isra\u00ebl aussi renomm\u00e9 qu\u2019Absalom pour sa beaut\u00e9; depuis la plante du pied jusqu\u2019au sommet de la t\u00eate, il n\u2019y avait point en lui de d\u00e9faut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.26","name":"2 Samuel 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.24","name":"2 Samuel 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.26","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:26","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019il se rasait la t\u00eate, c\u2019\u00e9tait chaque ann\u00e9e qu\u2019il se la rasait, parce que sa chevelure lui pesait, le poids des cheveux de sa t\u00eate \u00e9tait de deux cents sicles, poids du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.27","name":"2 Samuel 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.25","name":"2 Samuel 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.27","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:27","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Il naquit \u00e0 Absalom trois fils, et une fille nomm\u00e9e Tamar, qui \u00e9tait une femme belle de figure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.28","name":"2 Samuel 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.26","name":"2 Samuel 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.28","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:28","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Absalom demeura deux ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, sans voir la face du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.29","name":"2 Samuel 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.27","name":"2 Samuel 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.29","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:29","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Il fit demander Joab, pour l\u2019envoyer vers le roi; mais Joab ne voulut point venir aupr\u00e8s de lui. Il le fit demander une seconde fois; et Joab ne voulut point venir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.30","name":"2 Samuel 14:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.28","name":"2 Samuel 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.30","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:30","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Absalom dit alors \u00e0 ses serviteurs: Voyez, le champ de Joab est \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 du mien; il y a de l\u2019orge; allez et mettez-y le feu. Et les serviteurs d\u2019Absalom mirent le feu au champ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.31","name":"2 Samuel 14:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.29","name":"2 Samuel 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.31","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:31","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Joab se leva et se rendit aupr\u00e8s d\u2019Absalom, dans sa maison. Il lui dit: Pourquoi tes serviteurs ont-ils mis le feu au champ qui m\u2019appartient?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.32","name":"2 Samuel 14:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.30","name":"2 Samuel 14:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.32","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:32","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.014.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Absalom r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Joab: Voici, je t\u2019ai fait dire: Viens ici, et je t\u2019enverrai vers le roi, afin que tu lui dises: Pourquoi suis-je revenu de Gueschur? Il vaudrait mieux pour moi que j\u2019y fusse encore. Je d\u00e9sire maintenant voir la face du roi; et s\u2019il y a quelque crime en moi, qu\u2019il me fasse mourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.33","name":"2 Samuel 14:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.31","name":"2 Samuel 14:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.33","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 14:33","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.014.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.015.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.14.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Joab alla vers le roi, et lui rapporta cela. Et le roi appela Absalom, qui vint aupr\u00e8s de lui et se prosterna la face contre terre en sa pr\u00e9sence. Le roi baisa Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14","name":"2 Samuel 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.1","name":"2 Samuel 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.14.32","name":"2 Samuel 14:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.14.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb23e8565.24419360');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb23e8565.24419360\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb23e8565.24419360","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb23e8565.24419360'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb23e8565.24419360\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}